                   skos:definition "Accountable for a set of data and for managing associated metadata such as definitions, classifications, permitted uses, and data quality expectations."@en ;
                   skos:editorialNote "Definition adapted from Strengholt (Data Management at Scale), pp. 369–371."@en .


